Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.90,0:00:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.81,0:00:19.61,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Newdays 開始的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.68,0:00:23.74,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,給世界一個吻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.12,0:00:25.64,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Blowing in thewind
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.72,0:00:32.32,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,把一點點的勇氣和愛放進口袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.43,0:00:41.16,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,l wish如果我有翅膀的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.67,0:00:50.17,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不管悲傷、過去還是不安 都能夠飛越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.24,0:00:51.94,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,OhYeah！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.01,0:00:57.18,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有失去什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.79,0:01:00.69,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemyway！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.75,0:01:03.59,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,想用這掌心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.66,0:01:07.92,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住奇蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.00,0:01:16.73,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,朝向無盡的天空和大地 以及未來旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.80,0:01:19.93,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,剛長出的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.01,0:01:23.24,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh！ 一定 一定 一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.31,0:01:24.40,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.48,0:01:28.64,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,展現光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.09,0:01:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.52,0:01:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對著阻止你胡鬧的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.12,0:01:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是揮個拳頭開開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.89,0:01:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該不是真的想打架，對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.86,0:01:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.50,0:01:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就乖乖付帳回家去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.67,0:01:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.74,0:01:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是小小的玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.48,0:01:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.85,0:02:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老是麻煩你真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.68,0:02:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.55,0:02:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是幫了大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.15,0:02:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個，上個月的份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.35,0:02:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼晚才給你，真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.36,0:02:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.02,0:02:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我要收利息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.16,0:02:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賣剩的也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.73,0:02:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿伯母的三明治來做個交易吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.60,0:02:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人份的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.58,0:02:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#16 河畔的二重唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.72,0:02:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是正當防衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.92,0:02:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基亞特暗中持有移動要塞\N早就在準備即將來臨的戰爭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.36,0:02:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且，基亞特還擁護廢棄公主\N企圖毀滅這個世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.43,0:02:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須勇於面對\N基亞特的侵略行為才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.20,0:02:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，將軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.54,0:03:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我國和基亞特長久以來\N都維持著友好的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.17,0:03:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次可是基亞特先發動攻擊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.94,0:03:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史基特已經毀滅\N也沒有進一步攻打我國的徵兆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.51,0:03:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為沒有意義再戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.75,0:03:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想要我\N推翻我自己的決定嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.99,0:03:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無法命令我的部隊\N去打這種戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.19,0:03:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男爵夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.39,0:03:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳卸下特務部隊指揮官之位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.56,0:03:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史達姆少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.83,0:03:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.80,0:03:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即日起你連升兩級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.60,0:03:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後由你兼任指揮特務部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.17,0:03:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今尚未確認廢棄公主已死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.34,0:03:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，隨著用法的不同\N毀滅世界的劇毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.61,0:03:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以變成奪取世界霸權的王牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.42,0:03:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先傾全軍之力追捕廢棄公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.59,0:03:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要把公主抓到手\N這場戰爭必能獲勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.47,0:04:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.57,0:04:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.31,0:04:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了，對不對？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.55,0:04:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋\N快點把門關上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.48,0:04:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要扔東西也選一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.66,0:04:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了，撿到了一個奇怪的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.86,0:04:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有死...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.36,0:04:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對沒有死...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.00,0:04:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為秩序守護者那幫人也在找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.07,0:04:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣你會累倒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.21,0:04:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想比秩序守護者\N早一步找到你的妹妹和姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.61,0:04:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就應該以最有效率的方式\N保持萬全的身體狀態來面對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.48,0:04:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼效率不效率的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.65,0:04:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳只會說這種話嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.95,0:04:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要是毀了，妳再去找其他\N有因子的傢伙不就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.35,0:04:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不想經歷那種事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.09,0:05:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信我也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.93,0:05:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是這些話我還是想先說清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.76,0:05:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是自願待在你身邊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.93,0:05:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是因為義務，也不是為了使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.34,0:05:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能幫上你們的忙\N而自己選擇這麼做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.87,0:05:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.92,0:05:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.55,0:05:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.22,0:05:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得吃點東西才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.23,0:05:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到處都客滿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.53,0:05:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，那位小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有位子喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.70,0:05:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝爾肯斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳果然還活著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.17,0:05:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位小兄弟和小姐也在一起嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.01,0:05:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.91,0:05:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝爾肯斯先生為什麼到王都來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.88,0:05:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是被叫回教會本部來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.95,0:06:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們說從半個月前\N就掌握不到廢棄公主的行蹤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.85,0:06:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用奈落摧毀移動要塞之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.19,0:06:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王國軍拼命尋找廢棄公主的屍體\N卻怎麼也找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.33,0:06:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後就流傳著一個情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.76,0:06:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說在札威爾附近海岸\N有人目擊一位金髮藍眼的少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.07,0:06:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.40,0:06:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王國軍不再打算除掉廢棄公主\N反而變成要活捉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.81,0:06:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，不趕快找到廢棄公主的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.94,0:06:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會被打屁股的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.48,0:06:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道貝爾肯斯先生\N已經注意到帕希菲卡的事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.68,0:06:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，才不是那樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.05,0:06:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並不打算把那個小姐怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.42,0:06:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是已經吃膩鄉下料理了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.89,0:06:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道妳是一個人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.20,0:06:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我找了好久...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.87,0:06:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兄弟也不在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.07,0:06:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我想他們一定還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.94,0:06:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是人實在太多了\N想找也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.61,0:06:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找得我眼都花了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.51,0:06:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真是令人不放心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.45,0:07:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一見到貝爾肯斯先生\N我好像又有點精神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.12,0:07:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像爸爸就在身邊一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.96,0:07:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來陪妳吧，反正也沒事做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.03,0:07:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是不比教會還有王國軍\N早一步找到就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.03,0:07:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正船到橋頭自然直
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然很像我父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.14,0:07:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是雞蛋三明治耶\N看起來好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.31,0:07:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這點小事就高興成那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.38,0:07:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為最近都一直吃麵包和乳酪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.78,0:07:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近收入不好真是對不起妳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.25,0:07:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是怎麼來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.78,0:07:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在工作的地方要來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.48,0:07:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泡茶嗎？讓我來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.65,0:07:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要又燙到囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.32,0:07:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心，放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.79,0:07:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看吧，笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.43,0:07:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.10,0:07:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕美拉不是你初戀情人的名字吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.77,0:07:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我以前養的貓的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.54,0:07:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貓？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.31,0:08:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.01,0:08:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝完就走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.75,0:08:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來您有很深的煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方便的話，請到告解室來談談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.53,0:08:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我還在修行中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.76,0:08:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝妳的關心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.40,0:08:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜我不是瑪烏傑魯教的信徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.47,0:08:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.01,0:08:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管對象是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.51,0:08:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果放著眼前有煩惱的人不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.14,0:08:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那還能算是聖職人員嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.55,0:08:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實是我姊姊和妹妹下落不明...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.95,0:08:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那您一定很擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.69,0:08:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該找的地方都找過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.09,0:08:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他們不可能來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.16,0:08:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，還是抱著一絲希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.23,0:08:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起祈禱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.59,0:08:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望能早日平安找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.90,0:08:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有妳這份心意就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.17,0:08:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是我還是妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.57,0:09:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有立場期待神的庇祐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要在這裡待到什麼時候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你改變信仰了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是您的妹妹嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.31,0:09:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個不是，也許以前曾經是妹妹...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.58,0:09:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是個外人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.95,0:09:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是多一些像妳這樣的神官\N教會也許會有所改變吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.32,0:09:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.32,0:09:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要洗太久喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.49,0:09:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡妳也會想慢慢洗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.56,0:09:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次都是我等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.33,0:09:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳先回去不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.33,0:09:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就先回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.04,0:09:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服，好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.81,0:09:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷，我要出去了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.75,0:09:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方不要大聲叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.95,0:09:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好慢喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.28,0:09:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮都變冷了，我還特地洗的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.65,0:09:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.89,0:09:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.59,0:10:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了，下次來再還吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.03,0:10:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也不要拿給我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.34,0:10:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕美拉，妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.11,0:10:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時候我會夢到被人追趕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.61,0:10:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人追趕我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.28,0:10:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種夢誰都會作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.09,0:10:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.30,0:10:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被剝奪了指揮權？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.26,0:10:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男爵夫人好像違逆了將軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.17,0:10:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像由路克兼任我們的隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.84,0:10:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.07,0:10:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管去幾次柏拉赫男爵府邸\N裡面都說他不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.35,0:10:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許是我自己自作多情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為克里斯給我的信上寫著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.28,0:11:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"在玻璃峽谷看到的月亮真美"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.45,0:11:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.89,0:11:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯現在是不是一個人\N抬頭看著月亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.53,0:11:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什麼隱情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.46,0:11:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想想看，前幾天才發生大騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.53,0:11:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫克里斯的一定也很辛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.67,0:11:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會演變成戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.74,0:11:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有廢棄公主人在王都的傳言\N也開始流傳了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.84,0:11:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦，也去買這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.48,0:11:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.75,0:11:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦，偶爾也要吃吃點心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.19,0:11:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.40,0:11:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,買給妳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是想要嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.67,0:11:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.20,0:11:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天拿到了一點錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.24,0:11:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.31,0:11:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.45,0:12:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不奇怪也很怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.35,0:12:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.32,0:12:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先別管這個了，打工沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.92,0:12:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕，我都忘記了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.49,0:12:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐先生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.14,0:12:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.14,0:12:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.74,0:12:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果看我看到著迷的話\N不必客氣，你可以繼續看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.47,0:12:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自我意識過剩到這種程度\N也真是了不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.61,0:12:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.65,0:12:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才要想辦法改改\N自己老氣橫秋的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.75,0:12:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我去打工囉\N這個就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.75,0:12:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，公主殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.29,0:12:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.56,0:12:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來看啊，來看啊\N有笑有淚也有羅曼史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看完再付錢喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.96,0:12:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基塔夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.96,0:12:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，妳這身打扮\N簡直就是個清秀佳人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.17,0:12:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那表示我平常不是清秀佳人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戲差不多要開演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.14,0:13:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去準備吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.11,0:13:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.25,0:13:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.72,0:13:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要太過份\N給我滾到別的地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.19,0:13:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有選擇的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.56,0:13:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要還沒有確認律法破壞者已死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.83,0:13:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就會推定她還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.46,0:13:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然妳妹妹擁有\N不受我們探查的特性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.87,0:13:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我只好跟你同行以便監視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.84,0:13:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你們沒有能力找到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.11,0:13:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,維持現在這樣或許還比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.77,0:13:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說在前頭\N史黛雅的警告現在還是有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.18,0:13:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有律法破壞者\N身在王都的確實證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.85,0:13:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會一天殺死一萬人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.52,0:13:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經拼命在找了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.42,0:13:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少滿嘴自以為是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管賽菲莉絲還是娜塔莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.06,0:13:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然是兵器\N就像個兵器的樣子不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.09,0:13:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明有人的外貌\N動作也像人一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.03,0:14:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻毫不在乎地說著\N不像是人類會說出口的冷酷言語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.53,0:14:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確從你的角度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.24,0:14:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也許看起來是敵人\N也是冷酷無情的邪惡化身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.27,0:14:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，我們一開始就是這個世界\N以及人類這個種族的守護者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類的守護者？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.18,0:14:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺了那麼多人還敢說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.42,0:14:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要是顧全大局的必要行為\N我們不會猶豫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.96,0:14:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音她真的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.22,0:14:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經死了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.96,0:14:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這個怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.17,0:14:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喪失記憶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.17,0:14:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她現在叫自己帕美拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.90,0:14:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是弗雷取的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.11,0:14:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷？跟她在一起的那個男的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.34,0:14:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他救了帕希菲卡\N還把她安置在自己家裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.28,0:14:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什...什麼...\N那小子不就跟帕希菲卡同...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.62,0:14:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同居？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.28,0:14:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一起嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.55,0:14:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是碰巧在街上遇到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.02,0:14:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在已經不幹殺手\N在這裡當樂師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.09,0:15:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺手？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.49,0:15:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基塔夫先生以前因為某些原因\N追殺過帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.50,0:15:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說雷歐先生也知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡實際上是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.60,0:15:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薇妮雅小姐也知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.64,0:15:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我覺得在王都亂晃不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.81,0:15:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是告訴現在的她\N妳就是廢棄公主又太殘忍了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.11,0:15:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我拜託了戲團老闆\N讓她在這裡打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.62,0:15:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是多虧您照顧她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.35,0:15:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她負責馬的角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.69,0:15:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿上那個就沒有人會知道\N她是帕希菲卡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.93,0:15:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.93,0:15:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你也雇用我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.16,0:15:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐先生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.16,0:15:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要布偶裝的話我有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.80,0:15:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住，站住，站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.51,0:15:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的魔龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.88,0:15:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要代替瑪烏傑魯神來懲罰你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.15,0:15:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,演得很起勁嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.39,0:16:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.65,0:16:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢想成為搞笑演員的年輕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.42,0:16:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託我們一定要雇用他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.36,0:16:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還雇了新的女店員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.13,0:16:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得我們可以成為好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.97,0:16:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫帕美拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.40,0:16:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.60,0:16:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫薇妮雅，請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.34,0:16:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，觀眾都很喜歡你的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.04,0:16:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.04,0:16:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定可以成為一個優秀的丑角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.24,0:16:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問你叫...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.28,0:16:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫雷歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.45,0:16:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教，雷歐先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.82,0:16:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.62,0:16:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.85,0:16:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天也拜託妳囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.86,0:16:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還是不要打擾她比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.76,0:16:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定這樣比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.06,0:16:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣對她來說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.27,0:16:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們不嫌棄的話\N就在這個劇院過夜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.64,0:16:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.44,0:16:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.68,0:16:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？今天沒有打破盤子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.58,0:17:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.95,0:17:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你偶爾會帶著傷回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.58,0:17:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是挺笨手笨腳的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.82,0:17:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗盤子的工作也是很辛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.35,0:17:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得你老成得很不尋常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.49,0:17:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是18歲嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.29,0:17:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在軍隊待過一陣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.70,0:17:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才這種年紀，以前就當過軍人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.70,0:17:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只在軍中待了三年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.37,0:17:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是幹嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.24,0:17:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.24,0:17:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你買了衣服給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.78,0:17:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還收留我待在你家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.71,0:17:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我卻沒辦法替你做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.85,0:17:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，收留了這麼沒用的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.25,0:17:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.42,0:17:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,料理功夫很差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.86,0:17:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打掃偷工減料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.36,0:17:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泡個茶還會燙到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.09,0:17:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必說得那麼過份吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.93,0:17:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是妳剛剛自己承認的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.97,0:17:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.37,0:17:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看，兩個排在一起\N好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.07,0:17:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說了，趕快吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.54,0:17:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.54,0:18:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.88,0:18:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.75,0:18:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.78,0:18:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉蔻兒小姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.15,0:18:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.22,0:18:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在旅途中失散了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.32,0:18:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搭乘的船遇難，被拋進了海裡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.13,0:18:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.33,0:18:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在奈落的影響之下\N好像發生了不少船難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.47,0:18:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.07,0:18:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能再見到妳的姊姊和爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.91,0:18:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.97,0:18:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小女多虧您照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.81,0:18:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.21,0:18:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒做過什麼不正常的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.61,0:18:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.01,0:18:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.75,0:18:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡的未婚夫...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.98,0:18:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,類似這樣的身分啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.69,0:18:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以...我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是我們分手的時候了\N帕美拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.96,0:18:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.63,0:18:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分手？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳已經找到親人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.10,0:19:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.04,0:19:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算突然告訴我\N你是我爸爸什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.07,0:19:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是什麼都記不得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.87,0:19:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕美拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.91,0:19:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.74,0:19:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想留在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.41,0:19:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不可以留下來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.32,0:19:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.62,0:19:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方便的話，可以暫時讓\N這孩子留在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.69,0:19:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是只穿著身上這套衣服\N就被海浪沖走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.36,0:19:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還是住在旅館裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.93,0:19:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們聯絡到\N應該在王都的弟弟之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.67,0:19:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要再待一陣子就好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.54,0:19:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.27,0:19:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.54,0:19:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會偶爾過來看妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.85,0:19:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.12,0:19:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我女兒就交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.12,0:19:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.46,0:20:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我好久沒看到\N她那麼安心的表情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.26,0:20:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離開村子之後就一直被追殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且要是就這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.64,0:20:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在沒人知道她是\N廢棄公主的狀況下迎接生日的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷，你睡著了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.39,0:20:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.12,0:20:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我離開比較好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.22,0:20:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.39,0:20:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正就像撿了一隻流浪貓一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.33,0:20:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好過份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.83,0:20:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕美拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.47,0:20:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.70,0:20:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,河流的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.17,0:20:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以睡得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.54,0:20:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安，弗雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.01,0:20:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安，帕美拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.13,0:21:17.87,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,滋潤大地的雨水靜靜地飄下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.94,0:21:23.27,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,落在很遠很遠的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.34,0:21:30.58,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,將這愛的雨滴獻給 某個等待已久的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.65,0:21:36.28,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,清晨的微風吹過沾有雨滴的臉龐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.36,0:21:41.26,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,現在你感覺到什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.33,0:21:44.59,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,這雨滴有著明白的含意 比一切都還要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.66,0:21:49.73,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,就在那唯一的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.80,0:21:56.23,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,停駐在追趕著的雲影下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.31,0:21:59.64,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,在這心靈的旅程中想要找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.71,0:22:02.91,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不管到哪裡不管到哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.98,0:22:09.58,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天會再聽到熟悉的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.66,0:22:16.29,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,船將會啟航啟航 船會航行到哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.36,0:22:21.66,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯要相信廣闊的世界 到未知的海洋的盡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.73,0:22:28.83,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,你要前往遠方然後奔向未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.41,0:22:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分散在王都四處的卡蘇魯三兄妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.01,0:22:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂還是拼命在尋找大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.48,0:22:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉蔻兒雖然早一步遇見帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.68,0:22:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是好不容易找到的妹妹\N卻一直躲著她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.02,0:22:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡終於得到了\N她期望已久的平凡生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.19,0:22:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她能夠就這樣逃避到底嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.82,0:22:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主 下一回\N「短暫的世俗歌」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.16,0:22:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待